Package fr.sii.ogham.testing.extension.junit.sms.config

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PortConfig
    Provide configuration to build a provider that will provide a port for the server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FixedPortConfig
    Configuration that simply builds a FixedServerPortProvider that will in turn provide a fixed port.
    RandomPortConfig
    Configuration that builds a RandomServerPortProvider with the provided range of ports.
    ServerConfig
    Builder to generate a SimulatorConfiguration.
    SlowConfig  
  • Annotation Types Summary
